-- Christie Calls on Lawmakers to Approve Ban on Sick-Time Payouts by Jan. 9
-- B y   T e r r e n c e   D o p p
-- 2012-01-04T16:08:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/christie-calls-on-lawmakers-to-approve-ban-on-sick-time-payouts-by-jan-9.html
New Jersey  Governor  Chris Christie 
called on the Democratic-controlled Legislature to pass a ban on
payouts for unused sick time by the Jan. 9 end of the
legislative session.  Christie, a first-term Republican, spoke in  New Brunswick ,
New Jersey.  To contact the reporter on this story:
